WebLinks Launcher for BuiltWith

Effortlessly convert website URLs on BuiltWith.com into clickable links with this convenient Chrome extension. No more manual copying and pasting – simply open the page, and all website URLs listed under Builtwith website as it will automatically become clickable links that launch in a new tab.

Key Features:

- Automatically transforms website URLs on BuiltWith.com into clickable links
- Opens each website link in a new tab for seamless browsing
- Lightweight and efficient, with no unnecessary bloat or permissions required
- Easy to install and use, with no complicated setup or configuration needed

Whether you're a web developer, marketer, or just someone who wants to save time and effort by quickly accessing websites directly from BuiltWith.com with just a single click.

Compatible with the latest versions of Google Chrome and adhering to the Manifest V3 standards for enhanced security and privacy.

Install the WebLinks Launcher for BuiltWith today and unlock a more efficient way to explore websites on BuiltWith.com!
